From fd7bb91563effcde1243ad8c83b70b2992867093 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: KE4CON <ke4con@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Wed, 24 Jun 2026 17:54:20 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add unified settings-persistence service

- AppSettings aggregate + ConnectionSettings section, schema-versioned
- IAppSettingsStore + JsonAppSettingsStore: atomic temp-then-move writes,
  corruption-resilient per-section salvage load, forward-migration hook,
  one-time legacy station-profile.json import
- Route StationProfile.Load/Save through the unified store so there is a single
  source of truth, stored under the app config folder
- Register IAppSettingsStore in the desktop DI container for downstream use
- 12 tests: round-trip, defaults, salvage, atomicity, schema stamping, migration, legacy import
